  "english": [
    "The Gemara rejects this proof: <b>Perhaps</b> the sons of Rabbi Ḥiyya were referring to a case <b>where</b> one <b>tied knots</b> between the sets of windings even though there is no obligation to do so.",
    "<b>And Rabba says: Learn from it</b> that <b>the uppermost knot</b> in the ritual fringes is required <b>by Torah</b> law. <b>As, if</b> it <b>enters your mind</b> to say that it is <b>by rabbinic</b> law, whereas by Torah law it is sufficient to merely insert the strings into the hole without tying any knots, for <b>what</b> reason <b>was</b> it <b>necessary</b> for the Torah <b>to permit</b> placing wool <b>ritual fringes</b> on a linen <b>cloak?</b> It is <b>obvious</b> that it is permitted, since if <b>one attaches</b> a swatch of wool and a swatch of linen <b>with a single connection, it is not</b> considered <b>a connection</b> with regard to the prohibition against wearing a garment that includes both wool and linen. <b>Rather, learn from</b> it that the uppermost knot is required <b>by Torah law.</b>",
    "§ <b>Rabba bar Rav Adda says</b> that <b>Rav Adda says</b> that <b>Rav says: If a string was severed at its base,</b> i.e., where it is connected to the garment, the ritual fringes are <b>unfit. Rav Naḥman sat</b> in the study hall <b>and stated this <i>halakha</i>. Rava raised an objection to Rav Naḥman</b> from a <i>baraita</i>: <b>In what</b> case <b>is this statement said,</b> i.e., that there is a minimum length required for the strings? That is only when the strings are <b>initially</b> affixed to the garment. <b>But</b> in the <b>end,</b> i.e., after the strings are affixed in an acceptable manner, <b>its remainder and its severed</b> strings are fit at <b>any</b> length.",
    "The Gemara clarifies: <b>What</b> is <b>its remainder and what</b> are <b>its severed</b> strings? <b>What, is it not</b> that when the <i>baraita</i> mentions <b>its remainder</b> it is referring to a case <b>where</b> parts <b>of the</b> strings <b>were severed and</b> parts <b>of them remain, and</b> when the <i>baraita</i> mentions <b>its severed</b> strings it is referring to a case <b>where</b> the strings <b>were completely severed,</b> and nevertheless the strings are fit for the mitzva?",
    "The Gemara responds to Rava’s objection: <b>No,</b> the <i>tanna</i> of the <i>baraita</i> <b>is teaching one</b> <i>halakha</i>, and the <i>baraita</i> should be understood as follows: <b>The remainder of its severed</b> strings are fit at <b>any length.</b> The Gemara asks: If so, <b>let</b> the <i>baraita</i> simply <b>say: Its severed</b> strings are fit at any length; <b>why do I</b> need the mention of <b>its remainder? This teaches us that we require a remainder of its severed</b> strings long <b>enough to</b> wrap them around the other strings and <b>tie them in a slipknot.</b>",
    "§ <b>Rabba sat</b> in the study hall <b>and said in the name of Rav:</b> The <b>string</b> used <b>for winding</b> around the other strings <b>is counted in the quota</b> of ritual fringes, i.e., it is one of the eight strings on each corner, and there is no need to have an additional string for winding. <b>Rav Yosef said to</b> Rabba: <b>Shmuel said it, and not Rav.</b> This <b>was also stated</b> by another <i>amora</i>: <b>Rabba bar bar Ḥana says: Rabbi Yoshiya of Usha told me</b> that the <b>string</b> used <b>for winding</b> around the other strings <b>is counted in the quota</b> of ritual fringes.",
    "<b>Rava sat</b> in the study hall <b>and said in the name of Shmuel:</b> If one <b>wound the majority of</b> the white and the <b>sky-blue</b> strings instead of leaving the larger portion of the strings hanging loose beyond the windings, the ritual fringes are nevertheless <b>fit. Rav Yosef said to</b> Rava: <b>Rav said it, and not Shmuel.</b> The Gemara supports Rav Yosef’s version from that which <b>was also stated: Rav Huna bar Yehuda says</b> that <b>Rav Sheshet says</b> that <b>Rav Yirmeya bar Abba says</b> that <b>Rav says:</b> If one <b>wound the majority of</b> the white and the <b>sky-blue</b> strings, the ritual fringes are nevertheless <b>fit.</b>",
    "<b>Rav Ḥiyya, son of Rav Natan, teaches</b> this discussion <b>like this: Rav Huna says</b> that <b>Rav Sheshet says</b> that <b>Rav Yirmeya bar Abba says</b> that <b>Rav says:</b> If one <b>wound the majority of</b> the white and the <b>sky-blue</b> strings, the ritual fringes are nevertheless <b>fit. And even</b> if <b>he wound only one set of</b> windings, the ritual fringes are <b>fit. But</b> the <b>finest</b> way to affix the white and <b>sky-blue</b> strings is to ensure that <b>one-third</b> of the length of the strings is <b>windings and two-thirds</b> are <b>loose</b> hanging strings.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>And what</b> is the <b>measure</b> of <b>a set</b> of windings? It <b>is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i> that <b>Rabbi</b> Yehuda HaNasi <b>says:</b> It is <b>such that one winds</b> once <b>and</b> winds <b>a second and third</b> time, i.e., each set must contain at least three windings. It was <b>taught: One who minimizes</b> the sets of windings <b>may not</b> have <b>fewer than seven</b> sets, <b>and one who adds</b> to this number of sets <b>may not</b> have <b>more than thirteen</b> sets of windings.",
    "The Gemara provides explanations for these guidelines: <b>One who minimizes</b> the sets of windings <b>may not</b> wind <b>fewer than seven</b> sets, <b>corresponding to</b> the <b>seven firmaments. And one who adds</b> to this number of sets <b>may not</b> wind <b>more than thirteen</b> sets of windings, <b>corresponding to</b> the <b>seven firmaments and</b> the <b>six air</b> spaces <b>between them.</b>",
    "It was <b>taught: When one begins</b> to form the windings, he <b>begins</b> winding <b>with a white</b> string. This is because the verse indicates that one first inserts “the fringe of <b>the corner”</b> (Numbers 15:38), i.e., the white strings, which are of the same <b>type</b> as the <b>corner</b> of the garment. <b>And when he concludes</b> the windings, <b>he concludes with a white</b> string, in accordance with the principle: <b>One elevates</b> to a higher level <b>in</b> matters of <b>sanctity and does not downgrade.</b>",
    "§ The Gemara relates: <b>Rav and Rabba bar bar Ḥana were sitting</b> together. <b>A certain man was passing by wearing a cloak that</b> was made <b>entirely of sky-blue</b> wool, <b>on which he had affixed</b> white and <b>sky-blue</b> strings,"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דִּלְמָא דְּאִיקְּטַר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2581\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר נחמני\">רַבָּה</span>: שְׁמַע מִינַּהּ, קֶשֶׁר",
      "segment_ids": [
        0,
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֶלְיוֹן דְּאוֹרָיְיתָא, דְּאִי סָלְקָא דַעְתָּךְ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">דְּרַבָ</span>ּנַן, מַאי אִיצְטְרִיךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְמִישְׁרֵי סָדִין בְּצִיצִית? פְּשִׁיטָא! הַתּוֹכֵף",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תְּכִיפָה אַחַת אֵינוֹ חִיבּוּר, אֶלָּא שְׁמַע",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִינַּהּ דְּאוֹרָיְיתָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-unknown\" data-sage-type=\"unknown\" title=\"Rabba bar Rav Adda\" data-authority-id=\"21390\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Rav Adda\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר רב אדא\">רַבָּה בַּר רַב אַדָּא</span> אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Mar bar Rav Adda, Amora\" data-authority-id=\"189\" data-full-name=\"Mar bar Rav Adda\" data-name-he=\"רב אדא\">רַב אַדָּא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>: אִם נִפְסַק הַחוּט מֵעִיקָּרוֹ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "פְּסוּלָה. יָתֵיב <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">רַב נַחְמָן</span> וְקָא אָמַר לְהָא שְׁמַעְתָּא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵיתִיבֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">לְרַב נַחְמָן</span>: בַּמֶּה דְּבָרִים אֲמוּרִים –",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בִּתְחִילָּתוֹ, אֲבָל סוֹפוֹ – שְׁיָרָיו",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְגַרְדּוּמָּיו כׇּל שֶׁהוּא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַאי שְׁיָרָיו וּמַאי גַּרְדּוּמָּיו?",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַאי לָאו ״שְׁיָרָיו״ – דְּאִיפְּסִיק מִינַּיְיהוּ וְאִישְׁתַּיַּיר",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִינַּיְיהוּ, ״גַּרְדּוּמָּיו״ – דְּאִיגַּרְדּוּם אִיגַּרְדּוֹמֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לָא, חֲדָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קָתָנֵי, שַׁיּוֹרֵי גַּרְדּוּמָּיו כׇּל שֶׁהוּא. וְלֵימָא: ״גַּרְדּוּמָּיו״,",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״שְׁיָרָיו״ לְמָה לִי? הָא קָא מַשְׁמַע לַן, דְּבָעֵינַן שִׁיּוּרָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְגַרְדּוּמָּיו כְּדֵי לְעׇנְבָן. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>יָתֵיב <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2581\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר נחמני\">רַבָּה</span> וְקָאָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשְּׁמֵיהּ דְּרַב: חוּט שֶׁל כֶּרֶךְ עוֹלֶה מִן הַמִּנְיָן.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲמַר לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yosef I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1764\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yosef I\" data-name-he=\"רב יוסף בר חייא\">רַב יוֹסֵף</span>: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span> אַמְרַהּ וְלָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִיתְּמַר נָמֵי: אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2594\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר בר חנה\">רַבָּה בַּר בַּר חָנָה</span>, סָח לִי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">רַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יֹאשִׁיָּה דְּמִן אוּשָׁא: חוּט שֶׁל כֶּרֶךְ עוֹלָה לָהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִן הַמִּנְיָן. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>יָתֵיב <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span> וְקָא אָמַר מִשְּׁמֵיהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">דִּשְׁמוּאֵל</span>: תְּכֵלֶת שֶׁכָּרַךְ רוּבָּהּ – כְּשֵׁרָה. אֲמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yosef I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1764\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yosef I\" data-name-he=\"רב יוסף בר חייא\">רַב יוֹסֵף</span>: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span> אַמְרַהּ, וְלָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>. אִיתְּמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נָמֵי, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Huna bar Yehuda, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"917\" data-full-name=\"Rav Huna bar Yehuda\" data-name-he=\"רב הונא בר יהודה\">רַב הוּנָא בַּר יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Sheshet, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2938\" data-full-name=\"Rav Sheshet\" data-name-he=\"רב ששת\">רַב שֵׁשֶׁת</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yirmeya bar Abba I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1954\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yirmeya bar Abba I\" data-name-he=\"רב ירמיה בר אבא\">רַב יִרְמְיָה בַּר אַבָּא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>: תְּכֵלֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁכָּרַךְ רוּבָּהּ – כְּשֵׁרָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Ḥiyya, son of Rav Natan, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1123\" data-full-name=\"Ḥiyya, son of Rav Natan\" data-name-he=\"רב חייא בריה דרב נתן\">רַב חִיָּיא בְּרֵיהּ דְּרַב נָתָן</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַתְנֵי הָכִי: אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Huna I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"895\" data-full-name=\"Rav Huna I\" data-name-he=\"רב הונא\">רַב הוּנָא</span>, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Sheshet, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2938\" data-full-name=\"Rav Sheshet\" data-name-he=\"רב ששת\">רַב שֵׁשֶׁת</span>, אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yirmeya bar Abba I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1954\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yirmeya bar Abba I\" data-name-he=\"רב ירמיה בר אבא\">רַב יִרְמְיָה בַּר אַבָּא</span>, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>: תְּכֵלֶת שֶׁכָּרַךְ רוּבָּהּ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּשֵׁרָה, וַאֲפִילּוּ לֹא כָּרַךְ בָּהּ אֶלָּא חוּלְיָא אַחַת –",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּשֵׁרָה, וְנוֹיֵי תְכֵלֶת – שְׁלִישׁ גְּדִיל וּשְׁנֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁלִישֵׁי עָנָף. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְכַמָּה שִׁיעוּר חוּלְיָא? תַּנְיָא, רַבִּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹמֵר: כְּדֵי שֶׁיִּכְרוֹךְ וְיִשְׁנֶה וִישַׁלֵּשׁ. תָּאנָא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַפּוֹחֵת לֹא יִפְחוֹת מִשֶּׁבַע, וְהַמּוֹסִיף לֹא יוֹסִיף",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עַל שְׁלֹשׁ עֶשְׂרֵה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הַפּוֹחֵת לֹא יִפְחוֹת מִשֶּׁבַע,",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּנֶגֶד שִׁבְעָה רְקִיעִים, וְהַמּוֹסִיף לֹא יוֹסִיף עַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁלֹשׁ עֶשְׂרֵה, כְּנֶגֶד שִׁבְעָה רְקִיעִין וְשִׁשָּׁה",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲוִירִין שֶׁבֵּינֵיהֶם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּנָא: כְּשֶׁהוּא מַתְחִיל –",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַתְחִיל בַּלָּבָן: ״הַכָּנָף״ – מִין כָּנָף, וּכְשֶׁהוּא מְסַיֵּים –",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מְסַיֵּים בַּלָּבָן, מַעֲלִין בַּקּוֹדֶשׁ וְלֹא",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹרִידִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Ḥana, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2600\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Ḥana\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר חנה\">וְרַבָּה בַּר בַּר חָנָה</span> הֲווֹ יָתְבִי,",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הֲוָה קָא חָלֵיף וְאָזֵיל הָהוּא גַּבְרָא דְּמִיכַּסֵּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "גְּלִימָא דְּכוּלֵּהּ תְּכֵלְתָּא, וּרְמֵי לֵיהּ תְּכֵלְתָּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דִּלְמָא דְּאִיקְּטַר.</b> כלומר ממאי דצריך להקשר בכל חוליא דלמא הא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמרי דבי רבי חייא ה\"ק אם קשר על כל חוליא וחוליא הוו גרדומין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כשרין אבל ברוב ציציות לא קא מכשרי גרדומין דרוב ציציות אין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נקשרים על כל חוליא וחוליא: <b>קֶשֶׁר עֶלְיוֹן.</b> היינו נמי ההוא קשר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למטה הלכה למשה מסיני כלומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קשר אחד בציצית מיהא דאורייתא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולהכי נקט עליון משום דאי לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עביד אלא חד קשר בסופו עביד ליה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמקיים את הגדיל כולו: <b>דְּאוֹרָיְיתָא.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואפי' יכול לכרוך יפה ולהתקיים בלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קשר יום או יומים פסולה: <b>דְּאִי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">מדרבנן</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">למה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לי</span> לְמִישְׁרֵי סָדִין בְּצִיצִית.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכתיב לא תלבש שעטנז וסמיך ליה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גדילים תעשה לך (דברים כב) פשיטא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמותר: <b>התוכף תכיפה.</b> תופר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תחיבה אחת אינו חיבור משום ההיא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תחיבה שתוחב החוטין בטלית אינו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חיבור: <b>מעיקרו.</b> היינו ראש המחובר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לטלית: <b>במה דברים אמורים.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דבעינן שיעור לציצית כדאמרינן לקמן (מנחות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דף מא:) כמה תהא משולשלת כו':",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בתחלתו.</b> בשעת עשייה אבל בסופו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כגון אם נפסק לאחר זמן: <b>מאי לאו.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>שיריו.</b> דאיפסיק מינייהו קצת מחוטיו ."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונשאר קצת גרדומין: <b>דאיגרדם.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>איגרדומי.</b> ולגמרי נפסק צד העיקר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וקשיא למאן דאמר נפסק החוט"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מעיקרו פסולה:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>הָא <span class=\"dh-divergent\">קמשמע</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לַן.</b> מדתני שיריים בגרדומין משמע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלהוי בגרדומים שיורא קצת שיהיו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נקרא שירים כדי לעונבן כדפרישית",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעיל והאי כל שהוא דקתני כדי עניבה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>חוּט שֶׁל כֶּרֶךְ.</b> אותו שכורך סביב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ועושה ממנו הגדיל עולה ממנין שמונה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חוטין דשמונה חוטין בעינן כדמפרש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקמן (<a href=\"/menachot/42a\">מנחות מב.</a>): <b>תְּכֵלֶת</b> זהו שם כל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הציצית: <b>שֶׁכָּרַךְ רוּבָּהּ.</b> שעשה שני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלישי גדיל ושליש ענף כשרה ואע\"ג",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמצותה שליש גדיל ושני שלישי ענף",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כדאמרינן לקמן: <b>אֶלָּא חוּלְיָא אַחַת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הקפה ג' פעמים: <b>וְנוֹיֵי תְכֵלֶת.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:8:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עיקר מצות ציצית שליש גדיל ושני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:8:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלישי ענף: <b>לֹא יִפְחוֹת מִשֶּׁבַע</b> חוליות:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ששה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אוירים</span>.</b> שבין שבעה רקיעים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ועל שם שהתכלת דומה לים וים דומה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לרקיע כדלקמן (<a href=\"/menachot/43b\">מנחות דף מג:</a>) מדמי סידורה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לסידור הרקיעים כדי לזכרנו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לטובה שאף צבעה כמו כן נזקק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לציצית: <b>כְּשֶׁהוּא מַתְחִיל <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לכרוך</span> מַתְחִיל</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בַּלָּבָן.</b> שמניח שני חוטין ארוכין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעשות מהן הגדיל ומתחיל לכרוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בלבן ובאמצע כורך של תכלת וחוזר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ומסיים בלבן: <b>מִין כָּנָף.</b> תחילה ואח\"כ פתיל תכלת והאידנא דעבדינן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חמשה קשרים היינו דאמרינן (שם) שקולה מצות ציצית ככל התורה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כולה הלכך עבדינן שני קשרים מלמעלה ושלשה מלמטה משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מעלין בקדש ואין מורידין וכיון דאקדמה קרא למין כנף שמע מינה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חשוב הוא הלכך אי מסיים בתכלת הוה ליה מוריד סוף הציצית",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:11:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתחילתה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">דכוליה</span> תְּכֵלְתָּא.</b> כל הטלית: <b>ורמי</b> <b>ליה</b> <b>תכלתא.</b> ציצית:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Menachot 39a:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    }
  ],
  "tosafot": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>קֶשֶׁר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">העליון</span>.</b></big> בקונטרס פירש שני פירושים אחד אחר הגדיל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "380px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונקרא עליון כמו (<a href=\"/niddah/13a\">נדה דף יג.</a>) למעלה מן העטרה וזה אינו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מוכח אלא דמיהא בעינן קשר ול''א פירש סמוך לכנף אבל קשר שאחר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הגדיל כיון שרחוק מן הטלית משום ההוא לא הוי כלאים ותימה להאי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמוכח היכי מסיק ביבמות (<a href=\"/yevamot/4b\">דף ד:</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למאן דלא דריש סמוכים אלא היכא (דמוכח) [צ\"ל דמופנה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צאן קדשים] דצמר ופשתים למה לי דכלאים [צ\"ל בציצית",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צאן קדשים] מתנא דבי רבי ישמעאל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמעינן דבגדיהם צמר ופשתים וכו'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והשתא קשר העליון לא שמעינן )וא''כ) [צ\"ל אלא משום דאם לא כן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רי\"א חבר] לא הוי כלאים ואיצטריך שפיר לאיתויי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צמר ופשתים לומר שיהא צריך לעשותם",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בענין שיהא בהם כלאים וי''ל דהכא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא מפיק מקרא דצמר ופשתים אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מגדיל ומוכח (דכלאים) [צ\"ל מכלאים צאן קדשים] דדרשה דגדיל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דרשה נכונה היא דבעינן גדיל טוב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אי נמי סוגיא דהתם אתיא כמאן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמר גדיל דווקא(ושמא דהתם) [צ\"ל וסוגיא דהכא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צאן קדשים] אתיא כמאן דאמר או גדיל או פתיל ופלוגתא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמוראי הוא בסמוך והכי נמי תימה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דבפרק המוצא תפילין (<a href=\"/eruvin/96b\">עירובין צו:</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משמע דבעינן שזורין ור''ת נמי פירש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאינו חייב על כלאים עד שיהא משזר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואם כן איצטריך טובא קרא דכלאים",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בציצית ויש לומר דבעלמא יליף ליה (מתכלת דבגדי כהונה) [צ\"ל תכלת דציצית",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתכלת דבגדי כהונה דבעינן שזורין צאן קדשים] וכיון דתכלת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שזור הוא הדין לבן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>דאיגרדום איגרדומי</b></big>. פירש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "160px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בקונטרס שנפסקו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לגמרי וקשה דהא כל שהוא קתני וצריך",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לומר דלצדדין קתני ולא קאי אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אשיריו ונראה לפרש מאי לאו שיריו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאיפסיק מינייהו כלומר שיש מן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "החוטים שנפסקו מעיקרם ואישתייר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מן השלימין נמי וגרדומיו דאיגרדמו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כולם והשתא לא קאי כל שהוא אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אגרדומיו והא דאיפסיק מינייהו הוי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "השתא כמו נפסק החוט מעיקרו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלעיל וכי האי גוונא קרי שיריו פרק",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קמא דסוכה (<a href=\"/sukkah/13a\">דף יג.</a>) גבי אזוב תחילתו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלשה וסופו שנים וצ''ע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>שירי גרדומיו כל שהוא</b></big>. פרק מי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "160px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמת (<a href=\"/menachot/150a\">ב&#x27;&#x27;ב דף קנ.</a>) הוה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מצי לאיתויי הך גבי הך דפריך וכל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היכא דתני כל שהוא לית ליה שיעורא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>לא יפחות משבע כנגד שבעה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "210px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רקיעים</b></big>. לפי שתכלת דומה לים",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וים דומה לרקיע ואנן דלית לן תכלת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא קפדינן בהא והא נמי דאמרינן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צריך לקשור על כל חוליא וחוליא היינו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כדי שיהא ניכר התכלת ומה שאנו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נוהגים חמשה קשרים פירש בקונטרס (גבי) [צ\"ל דהא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שיטה מקובצת] ציצית שקולה כנגד כל המצות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לפי שציצית עולה ת''ר וח' חוטין וחמשה קשרים עולה תרי''ג ומיהו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כל ציצית האמורים בפרשה חסירים יו''ד ויש לומר שיש פסוק והיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לכם לציצית וג' ציצית כתובים בפרשה ולמ''ד זו משלימתן וכן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נוהג רבינו תם לעשות אותן ה' קשרים ב' בסמוך לטלית וג'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Menachot 39a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סמוך לפתיל משום מעלין בקדש ולא מורידין כדאמרינן שמסיים",
